### Optimizers API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/optimizers
### Auth: Bearer token required (Clerk JWT)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_clerk_jwt_token_here

### 1. Analyze content
POST {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/analyze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Check out our new product! 🚀 It's going to change everything.",
  "contentType": "caption",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "goals": ["engagement", "viralPotential"]
}

### 2. Optimize content
POST {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/optimize
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Check out our new product! 🚀 It's going to change everything.",
  "contentType": "caption",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "currentScore": 65,
  "goals": ["engagement"]
}

### 3. Get hashtag suggestions
POST {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/hashtags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Behind the scenes of our product development process",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "count": 10,
  "includeNiche": true
}

### 4. Generate A/B variants
POST {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/variants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Check out our new product! 🚀",
  "contentType": "caption",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "variantCount": 3,
  "aspects": ["hook", "cta"]
}

### 5. Get best posting times
GET {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/times?platform=instagram&timezone=America/New_York
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get optimization history
GET {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/history?limit=10&contentType=caption
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Generate creative prompts from idea (Idea Mode)
POST {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/prompts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "sunset beach yoga meditation",
  "mode": "idea",
  "targetMedia": "image",
  "count": 5
}

### 8. Generate creative prompts from idea (Video Mode)
POST {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/prompts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "futuristic city at night with neon lights",
  "mode": "idea",
  "targetMedia": "video",
  "count": 5,
  "styleHint": "cyberpunk aesthetic"
}

### 9. Generate prompt variations (Variation Mode)
POST {{baseUrl}}/optimizers/prompts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "A majestic eagle soaring through dramatic clouds at golden hour, cinematic lighting, photorealistic, 8K detail",
  "mode": "variation",
  "targetMedia": "image",
  "count": 3
}

